Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.02,0:00:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.56,0:00:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.67,0:00:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.88,0:00:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.68,0:00:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.96,0:01:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.40,0:01:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.71,0:01:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.39,0:01:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团为了统治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以无人操纵MD为主要军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,创立新生OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于反对财团的功利主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的所有权力被夺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,组织形态出现改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但藉着MD的高性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们决速地扩大了支配地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于宇宙卫星认同了财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团下令杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.52,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全孤立的钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对他们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历史的洪流继续不断倒流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.74,0:02:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗，然后活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.64,0:02:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你，你们还不可以死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.68,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十四话\N[它的名字是次代]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此为止吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.01,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派全军覆没的\N消息来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…那方面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投入那么庞大的兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们为何还能支持下去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹01出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD部队也失去了半数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在好像进入了混战状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怕特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被带走也只是时间的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办?侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知未出动的所有地面部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上前去卢森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.71,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭特列斯派和钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.65,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯始终只是迷惑士兵的虚像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.15,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和当作叛乱份子像征的钢弹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.69,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N无论如何要阻止他们联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.51,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核对声纹和指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请说出姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.73,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,资料核对确认，请入内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你终于来了，希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我亲爱的和平使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心欢迎你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是特列斯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，开枪杀我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了结束战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?只要我一日在世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗就不会结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那样想才来到这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我让我进来的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是数月前\N预先输入电脑的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为我终有一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会和包括你在内的钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.47,0:06:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽情畅谈一番呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对你没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.77,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们只是想着和平就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个地球的…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.78,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括地球在内的\N整个宇宙的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想着战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平只是战斗结束后的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我问你\N你的敌人是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吗?OZ吗?罗姆斐拉财团吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是那些出卖了\N你们的遥远故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.87,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在我面前\N要取我性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种战斗没结果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你的敌人就是命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我会战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，何时死去也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想享受自己的命运吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.49,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特比你坚强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不到你会在继续战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感到极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但事实上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无人能改变这个时代的演变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就能改变吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前掌握了历史的主导权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再做一次同样的事就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没那心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和你畅谈的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.89,0:08:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我人生里最大的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.89,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你一定要同生共死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.23,0:08:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相赏识后，被神召见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙不轻易死心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不怕死的士兵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为那姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是正常人类正确的战斗方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.48,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在，你不知道谁是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.02,0:08:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面和我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的战斗也已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本未结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.89,0:08:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了你，许多士兵也正在死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少，你的战斗未结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果结束了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，要结束的只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.94,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍在继续的悲痛\N而徒然的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你不要再令我伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.22,0:09:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以和我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有指示你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后生存方式的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是稻草人五号\N发现飞翼O
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在开始工程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装上这么多，没问题了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是能炸毁三部里欧的份量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，返回里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然想炸毁它吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然吧，因为对OZ来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，对罗姆斐拉来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,称为钢弹的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是会成为支配的障碍的虚像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把真正的价值告诉他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，现在炸毁飞翼O
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现物体高速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯!闪电伯爵来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是稻草人五号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴尔吉!托尔吉斯出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何逃避战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD令战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连战斗方式也忘记了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是\N我的思想已经落后了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心，杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的高速输送船正接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.29,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,预知我会来而摆出的阵势吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在倚赖MD的战斗上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.93,0:11:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是理所当然的战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备很周详啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援军吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们看来对我评价过高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.22,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,7号机至12号机在后方散开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的，闪电伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠你，我才能战斗到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你告别令我伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，现在要战斗到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永别了，托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的爱机，安息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆了?他打算逃亡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会让他那样做吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.65,0:14:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗? 他打算转乘飞翼O吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.09,0:14:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闪电伯爵看来也失策了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指示MD更改目标…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给他更匹配的死法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在极乐世界咀咒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的天真决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是稻草人五号，任务完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭了飞翼O和托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同时杀了杰克斯‧马吉斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们看来对飞翼O评价过低了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好!这种反应速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种战斗能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为完美战士的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.49,0:15:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会被那部可怕的机体玩弄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我祈求你选择的路\N是正确的路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，不，米利亚尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.50,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是通向和平的路标\N匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.44,0:16:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我给它命名为[次代钢弹]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部机体会让驾驶员看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.92,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人的模样和驾驶员本身的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本没有可以选择的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你驾驶这机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.56,0:16:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我有同一结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就一起跟这世界道别吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为了什么造这种东西出来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人类的存在意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不能从那里找到答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我的战斗结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我一定要从\N名为战斗的行动里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到解答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为达到那目的的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为钢弹最有资格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.72,0:17:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我想给予胜利者的战败者祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是令那心愿\N有可能实现的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以为自己制造了神吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战士有单纯的战斗心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部次代钢弹就会有\N消除迷惘的机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不迷惘的战士崇高而美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在某意思上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.74,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得上最接近神的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.88,0:17:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不信神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看你的战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.88,0:17:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看你的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯，我先忠告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘坐那机体后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以当胜利者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次代钢弹也不是兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它希望你成为战败者回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有那心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.22,0:18:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，在杀死我之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不准你擅自寻死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我解除了自爆装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!\N敌人的数目完全没减少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的迪尔麦优不断派增援来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别放弃!战斗没有结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续战斗才有意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六时方向发现物体高速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援军吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是资料上没记录的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!那是…自己人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.40,0:20:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的敌人…不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些人只是被迫战斗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好机会!攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.84,0:20:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么…是这些人吗…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.62,0:20:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一样…这部机体和O一样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把一切消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.57,0:20:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗的人全是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.46,0:21:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，请你答应我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.46,0:21:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.47,0:21:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本没有可以选择的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的…我的未来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的死亡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看见你的未来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.41,0:21:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.85,0:22:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯…我…没那资格…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.43,0:22:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.55,0:22:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.55,0:22:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.55,0:22:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.55,0:22:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.05,0:22:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.55,0:23:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.05,0:23:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.55,0:23:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.55,0:23:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.38,0:23:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔为了和罗姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.48,0:23:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日益增加的压力对抗\N他前去领取沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.05,0:23:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯希望和钢弹驾驶员\N并肩作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.02,0:23:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上回到故乡卫星的五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.29,0:23:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但再次被选为完成了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.16,0:23:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[双龙钢弹]驾驶员的五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.93,0:23:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把杰克斯看作敌人，挑战他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.07,0:23:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第三十五话\N五飞复出

